snippet.title: Erzurum - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Erzurum is a winter survival game, will release on January, 2021. For more information, please check the Steam page : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1392060/Erzurum/

Song / Türkü : Karadır Kaşların Ferman Yazdırır
Türkü, Çağlar İçer tarafından kaydedilmiştir.
Çağlar İçer Youtube kanalı : https://youtu.be/VXc4T6IlbUE
